 hand represent the active part of us that use the information received to create the physical reality of our lives when the two are working together well we have balance and experience awareness leading to peace and productivity see also parents try posting your dream on dreamcrowd for a free interpretation Carl Jung Dream Sigmund Freud Unconscious mind Narcissism Psychoanalysis Myers-Briggs Type Indicator Milton H. Erickson The Shining (film) Consciousness Meaning of life Carlos Castaneda EastEnders Lucid dreaming Simone Weil Out-of-body experience Human Sin City The Amber Spyglass Infantilism Gnosticism W.I.T.C.H. Edgar Cayce Gender role Scientology beliefs and practices Arthur Schopenhauer Economic inequality Socrates Scenes from a Memory Art Jiddu Krishnamurti Modernism Force (Star Wars) Yoga Sutras of Patanjali Collective unconscious Transactional analysis Artificial consciousness Science Soul Sleep Autism Oneiromancy Psychology of religion Avenue Q Cognitive science Grief Tarot Fictional character Mantra A Course In Miracles Philosophy of perception Religion Abortion debate Polyamory The Death Gate Cycle Domestic violence James Hillman BDSM Origin belief Michel Henry Main characters of Fullmetal Alchemist Sri Aurobindo Gestalt therapy Eastern Orthodox Church Cyberspace Jungian psychology Karen Horney Friedrich Schleiermacher Reality Cliff Richard Fathers' rights Humphrey Bogart Ethics Philosophy of mathematics God Emperor of Dune The Fairly OddParents Social rule Irna Phillips Yin and yang Franz Boas Discordianism Sant Thakar Singh Traumatic brain injury Christian eschatology Jon Secada Current teachings of Prem Rawat Nocturnal emission Episodes of Lost (Season 1) K' Animism God Comparing and contrasting Judaism and Christianity Urantia Transsexuality 